eu.itesla_project.iidm.network

Interface Bus

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Identifiable

    public interface Bus
extends Identifiable
    A bus is a set of equipemnts connected together through a closed switch. It could be a configured object ot a result of a computation depending of the context.
    Author:
    Geoffroy Jamgotchian
